 powerful card synergies to combine the unique abilities of your three heroes.<br><br><img src=\"https:\/\/cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com\/steam\/apps\/1038370\/extras\/Witch_Header_v1.png?t=1646808341\" \/><br><br><img src=\"https:\/\/cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com\/steam\/apps\/1038370\/extras\/Sshot_Inventory1.png?t=1646808341\" \/><br><br>Outside of combat encounters, the party's loadout of weapons, items and gear can be swapped or upgraded.<br><br><img src=\"https:\/\/cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com\/steam\/apps\/1038370\/extras\/Sshot_LongShot_v1.png?t=1646808341\" \/><br><br>New items and weapons are discovered while exploring the vast overworld of Ashe.<br><br><img src=\"https:\/\/cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com\/steam\/apps\/1038370\/extras\/Warlord_Header_v1.png?t=1646808341\" \/><br><br>Traverse an immense overworld map and author a unique adventure in a dangerous hunt for resources critical to the survival of Terralin. <br><br>Every journey you take will be a Trial.<br><br><img src=\"https:\/\/cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com\/steam\/apps\/1038370\/extras\/TrialsOfFire_SShot_Assassin_v2.jpg?t=1646808341\" \/><br><br><a href=\"https:\/\/steamcommunity.com\/linkfilter\/?url=https:\/\/discord.gg\/C769v4n\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"  ><img src=\"https:\/\/cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com\/steam\/apps\/1038370\/extras\/DiscordLogo_v5.png?t=1646808341\" \/><\/a>","about_the_game":"Trials of Fire is a tactical, deck-building adventure game set in a fantasy world in ruin.<br><br><img src=\"https:\/\/cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com\/steam\/apps\/1038370\/extras\/ToF_HeroLoop_v1.png?t=1646808341\" \/><br><br>Savage combat and tough decisions await in the unforgiving wastelands of Ashe.<br><br>Trials of Fire combines overworld exploration, multi-character combat and loot linked deck-building to create fresh strategic options on every run. <br><br><img src=\"https:\/\/cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com\/steam\/apps\/1038370\/extras\/TrialsOfFire_SShot_SPSpkr_v3.jpg?t=1646808341\" \/><h2 class=\"bb_t